          label="Demo: building a bid estimate in BuildWorkPro with line items, material and labor cost items from the catalog, and margin applied on the Rates tab"
          caption="Takeoff quantities become bid line items in BuildWorkPro — material and labor cost items roll up per line, and margin, commission, and overhead apply on the Rates tab."
        />
